ordia Crescit</div></strong></span>[/black]</span><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.arsenal.com/sites/default/files/wallpaper/facup2017_2_1920x1080_0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arsenal.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fwallpaper%2Ffacup2017_2_1920x1080_0.jpg&h=41c70e98&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://paininthearsenal.com/wp-content/uploads/getty-images/2017/08/826971802-chelsea-v-arsenal-the-fa-community-shield.jpg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpaininthearsenal.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fgetty-images%2F2017%2F08%2F826971802-chelsea-v-arsenal-the-fa-community-shield.jpg.jpg&h=c4697e47&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/FFBXeiT4RtI/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FFFBXeiT4RtI%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=c295d061&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DbRi5-HXcAEu1wU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDbRi5-HXcAEu1wU.jpg&h=757f0613&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/31044106_10155933080632713_296830081794310144_o.jpg?_nc_cat=0&amp;oh=ccfd4a8f9fd02877b2ee059287d4a56f&amp;oe=5B72400A\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F31044106_10155933080632713_296830081794310144_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D0%26oh%3Dccfd4a8f9fd02877b2ee059287d4a56f%26oe%3D5B72400A&h=7f148e7b&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://www.arsenal.com/sites/default/files/styles/large_16x9/public/images/wenger_22.jpg?itok=hAHxCoZv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.arsenal.com%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Flarge_16x9%2Fpublic%2Fimages%2Fwenger_22.jpg%3Fitok%3DhAHxCoZv&h=152b320c&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em>&quot;To all the Arsenal lovers. Take care of the values of the club.  <br />\nMy love and support for ever.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nArsene Wenger</em></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有請風光廿貳載阿仙奴名帥</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/w4688178656w128.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fw4688178656w128.jpg&h=d2d575c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">阿仙尼，雲加</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/213754_da30fdcb9f39f68cc6ec0f9f7f7eec0c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F213754_da30fdcb9f39f68cc6ec0f9f7f7eec0c.jpg&h=606008ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n[center]<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">曾三奪英格蘭足球超級聯賽冠軍</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/214236_895ccefe702ac640b283609810781737.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F214236_895ccefe702ac640b283609810781737.jpg&h=91d3f9c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n[red]<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">其中一次係115年來首支於頂級聯賽保持全季不敗的球隊</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/20/214411_45d39a870319d68046b73c85a1259660.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F20%2F214411_45d39a870319d68046b73c85a1259660.jpg&h=8fa94941&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span s